{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"XPathEvaluator","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XPathEvaluator","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","browserCompat":["api.XPathEvaluator"],"sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><em><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XPathEvaluator\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>XPathEvaluator</code></a></em></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XPathEvaluator/XPathEvaluator\"><code>XPathEvaluator()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Instance methods</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XPathEvaluator/createExpression\"><code>createExpression()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XPathEvaluator/createNSResolver\"><code>createNSResolver()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XPathEvaluator/evaluate\"><code>evaluate()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","sidebarMacro":"APIRef","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>The <code>XPathEvaluator</code> interface allows to compile and evaluate <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/XPath\">XPath</a> expressions.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"constructor","title":"Constructor","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"xpathevaluator\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XPathEvaluator/XPathEvaluator\" title=\"XPathEvaluator()\"><code>XPathEvaluator()</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Creates a new <code>XPathEvaluator</code> object.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"instance_methods","title":"Instance methods","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"xpathevaluator.createexpression\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XPathEvaluator/createExpression\"><code>XPathEvaluator.createExpression()</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Creates a parsed XPath expression with resolved namespaces.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"xpathevaluator.creatensresolver\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XPathEvaluator/createNSResolver\"><code>XPathEvaluator.createNSResolver()</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Adapts any DOM node to resolve namespaces allowing the XPath expression to be evaluated relative to the context of the node where it appeared within the document.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"xpathevaluator.evaluate\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XPathEvaluator/evaluate\"><code>XPathEvaluator.evaluate()</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Evaluates an XPath expression string and returns a result of the specified type if possible.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Example","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"count_the_number_of_div_elements","title":"Count the number of <code>&lt;div&gt;</code> elements","isH3":true,"content":"<p>The following example shows the use of the <code>XPathEvaluator</code> interface.</p>\n<h4 id=\"html\">HTML</h4>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><p class=\"example-header\"><span class=\"language-name\">html</span></p><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>XPath example<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Number of <span class=\"token entity named-entity\" title=\"<\">&amp;lt;</span>div<span class=\"token entity named-entity\" title=\">\">&amp;gt;</span> elements: <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>output</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>output</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"javascript\">JavaScript</h4>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><p class=\"example-header\"><span class=\"language-name\">js</span></p><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> xpath <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"//div\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> evaluator <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">XPathEvaluator</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> expression <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> evaluator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createExpression</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>xpath<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> result <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> expression<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">evaluate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n  document<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  XPathResult<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">ORDERED_NODE_SNAPSHOT_TYPE</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\ndocument<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"output\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textContent <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> result<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>snapshotLength<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"result\">Result</h4><div class=\"code-example\" id=\"sect1\"><p class=\"example-header\"></p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"count the number of div elements sample\" id=\"frame_count_the_number_of_div_elements\" width=\"100%\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://localhost:5042/en-US/docs/Web/API/XPathEvaluator/runner.html?id=count_the_number_of_div_elements\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>","titleAsText":"Count the number of <div> elements"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#interface-xpathevaluator","title":"DOM Standard"}],"query":"api.XPathEvaluator"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.XPathEvaluator"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/createExpression\"><code>document.createExpression()</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XPathExpression\"><code>XPathExpression</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Constructor","id":"constructor"},{"text":"Instance methods","id":"instance_methods"},{"text":"Example","id":"example"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"The XPathEvaluator interface allows to compile and evaluate XPath expressions.","popularity":0,"modified":"2023-07-07T07:19:19.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/xpathevaluator","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/main/files/en-us/web/api/xpathevaluator/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://gi